" SplitJoin {{{ "
  function! BreakHere()
    s/\(.\{-}\)\(\s*\)\(\%#\)\(\s*\)\(.*\)/\1\r\3\5
    call histdel("/", -1)
  endfunction

  nnoremap <silent> sk :SplitjoinSplit<CR>
  nnoremap <silent> sj :SplitjoinJoin<CR>
  nnoremap <silent> J mzJ`z
  nnoremap <silent> S :call BreakHere()<CR>
" }}} SplitJoin "

